			</a>
  </div>
  
 <div style="float: left;">
              <img title='Photo: , License: N/A' height='105' alt='23026.jpg' width='140' class='teaser-image' src='/polopoly_fs/1.324365.1323181912!/image/3682139456.jpg_gen/derivatives/box_w140/3682139456.jpg' />
